text: #Singapore which has one of Asia’s smallest populations is emerging with the region’s highest number of #coronavirus cases after #China and #India. The island-nation reported 931 new cases on Sunday, with the total number of infections exceeding 13,000, overtaking Japan https://t.co/k8oxD8Udkn
